column3: An assortment of seafood favorites, including shrimp, takoyaki, and salmon rolls.
A stir-fry featuring firm tofu, bell peppers, green onions and soy sauce over green beans and long-sliced carrots.
A cod fillet marinated in a miso glaze and grilled to perfection. Topped with sesame and soy sauces.
A rice dish featuring tender tako cuts mixed with seasonings. Served with tempura bits.
A swordfish steak grilled with a side of stir-fried seasonal veggies
